parameters: Unknown appeared decades ago...
At first, People were terrified.
Some even said it was end of the world...
However nothing happend for long time.
Life returned to normal
And slowly...curiosity began to replace fear
Everyday people discussed mystery of Unknown
"I heared there are tons of golds!"
"I heared there is dragon living there!"
"I heared..."
Soon, numerous people began expedition to Unknown and...
nobody came back
However, that was not the end of story
Monsters flooded out of Unknowns as if they smelled
bloods of innocent preys
and soon the world was filled with fear
our territory was destroyed and only small part is recovered
still today
After decades of hunting, monsters disappeared like nothing
happened
Only few monsters occasionally attacked villages
Even that was critical to humans...
From time to time, brave souls set out to uncover the secert
and remove source of fears
and we call them hero...
yet nobody was successful
There is hidden room located at west on 2nd floor.
You used to be able to find valuable items.
North of 2nd floor, two portal leads to either dungeon
or magicians room.
Path to King and Queens Room, which is at east of 2nd floor,
has been destroyed.

Elliot
I think you got scammed.
As time passes, I can feel I am getting weaker...
Will I die...?
I have so many things left to do...
Seeing Queen's face allowed me to realize how old we are...
Today, old lady came and told me she could make us live
forever under one condition...
haha, I'm not fool so I kicked her out of my kingdom
Queen was in bed for weeks...
She barely can breath...
There should be way...
Last month, I told all my soldiers to look for that old lady
I need to find her
It really worked!
Queen is as healthy as her twenties...
So am I...
Looking at mirror was never this happy...
Today, I found my wife sucking bloods from deer I hunted...
and I couldn't resist but drink bloods spread around floor
What is going on? Is this the condition old lady told me?
I can hear him...I can hear the lord calling for us...
We must invite him here...
